# NAME: US_Brokers
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: US brokers rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-04
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include US brokers, US-routed trading venues, and US-specific trading or crypto brokerage services.
# RULE: Prefer dedicated domains/subdomains and keep broad keyword/domain rules conservative.
# RULE: When a broker does not publish stable public IP ranges, prefer official gateway and API hostnames over inferred IPs.

# ==================== Kraken ====================
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,kraken.com
DOMAIN,api.kraken.com
DOMAIN,docs.kraken.com
DOMAIN,support.kraken.com

